These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, soy-milk
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: marigold, iris, bellflower, rose, orchid, daffodil
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee  | iced-tea    | lemonade  | cola      | milk    |
| Flower      | iris  | daffodil | orchid | marigold | rose | bellflower |

