.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, rugby, tennis, surfing, biathlon
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, country, disco, electronic, house, techno
 1. the fan of disco is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the fan of country##1
 3. the fan of house is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 6. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
10. the person who's sport is tennis is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Sport         | tennis | biathlon | ice-hockey | surfing | rowing | rugby  |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | electronic  | disco  | classical | house      | country |

