.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, almond-milk, lemonade, coffee, iced-tea
There are 6 different nationalities: american, australian, brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
1. the mexican is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the chinese is on the left of the american##1
3. the chinese is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the australian is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the german is the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the brazilian##1
7. the american is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | almond-milk    | hot-chocolate | coffee     | cola   | lemonade     |
| Nationality   | german | australian | mexican | brazilian | chinese | american |

