.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-9::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, aristoff, havana, swisher, old-henry, cain
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
2. the havana-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the van is the bolivar-smoker##1
5. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
6. the cain-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
7. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
8. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
9. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Cigar    | old-henry | aristoff | swisher | cain    | bolivar | havana      |
| Transport   | ship   | bike     | bus      | subway | van           | snowmobile |

