.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, cranberry, kiwi, onion, peach, peas
There are 6 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk, milk, cola, fanta, water
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
7. the person eating peas is the person drinking sprite##1
8. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | cranberry | peas   | peach  | kiwi    | onion  | broccoli |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | sprite | water | fanta | milk | cola |

