House: cottage, victorian, wooden, art-deco, tower, craftsman
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the cottage house is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
4. the wooden house is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the victorian house is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking 7up is the art-deco house##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the tower house is on the left of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Beverage   | tea    | 7up     | juice | almond-milk | lemonade | mirinda   |
| House        | craftsman | art-deco | tower | wooden   | cottage    | victorian |

