.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-12::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: disaster, time-travel, fantasy, adventure, drama, superhero
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, bus, jet-ski, motorbike, scooter, van
1. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
9. the person driving the van is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | superhero | adventure    | time-travel | fantasy  | disaster |
| Transport     | bus    | scooter | motorbike | van   | jet-ski | bike    |

