.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-13::.
6 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, poker, chess, go, backgammon
The people use 6 different means of transport: car, motorbike, roller, scooter, tram, trike
1. the person playing chess is the person driving the roller##1
