3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person playing scrabble is the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
7. the person playing poker is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
8. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
9. the person playing backgammon is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |       3        |     4     |     5     |   6    |
| Game         | poker | snooker | go | chess | scrabble    | backgammon |
| Transport   | car   | tram      | scooter        | roller    | motorbike | trike  |

