4. the owner of the rat is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
