5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
6. the colombian is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the french is on the right of the polish##1
8. the polish is on the right of the malaysian##1
9. the malaysian is on the right of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | salsa     | rock       | house  | metal | country    |
